# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:23
msgid "Quick Tutorial"
msgstr "Brzi vodič"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:25
msgid ""
"Using OpenShot is very easy, and this tutorial will take you through the "
"basics in **under 5 minutes**. After this tutorial, you will be able to make "
"a simple photo slide-show with music."
msgstr ""
"Korištenje OpenShota je vrlo jednostavno, a ovaj vodič će vas provesti kroz "
"osnove u **manje od 5 minuta**. Nakon ovog vodiča moći ćete napraviti "
"jednostavnu prezentaciju fotografija s glazbom."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:30
msgid "Basic Terminology"
msgstr "Osnovna terminologija"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:31
msgid ""
"To help understand the steps below, here are some definitions of a few basic "
"terms used in this tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Kako biste bolje razumjeli korake u nastavku, ovdje su definicije nekoliko "
"osnovnih pojmova korištenih u ovom vodiču."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:38
msgid "Term"
msgstr "Pojam"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:38
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:40
msgid "Project"
msgstr "Projekt"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:40
msgid ""
"A **project** includes references to all the video files and edits "
"(animations, titles, etc...), saved in a single file."
msgstr ""
"**Projekt** uključuje reference na sve video datoteke i uređivanja "
"(animacije, naslove itd.), spremljene u jednoj datoteci."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:41
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "Vremenska crta"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:41
msgid ""
"The **timeline** is an editing user interface that represents edits and "
"clips on a horizontal ruler. Time progresses from left to right."
msgstr ""
"**Vremenska crta** je korisničko sučelje za uređivanje koje prikazuje "
"uređivanja i isječke na horizontalnoj ljestvici. Vrijeme napreduje s lijeva "
"na desno."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:42
msgid "Track"
msgstr "Staza"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:42
msgid ""
"A separate **layer** on the timeline, which can hold clips. A timeline is "
"made up of many tracks, stacked vertically."
msgstr ""
"Poseban **sloj** na vremenskoj crti koji može sadržavati isječke. Vremenska "
"crta sastoji se od više staza složenih okomito."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:43
msgid "Clip"
msgstr "Isječak"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:43
msgid ""
"A **trimmed** portion of video, audio, or both positioned on a track, and at "
"a specific position in time. When files are dropped on the timeline, they "
"are represented as a Clip."
msgstr ""
"**Izrezani** dio videa, zvuka ili oboje, postavljen na stazu i na određenoj "
"vremenskoj poziciji. Kada se datoteke povuku na vremensku crtu, prikazuju se "
"kao isječak."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:44
msgid "Transition"
msgstr "Prijelaz"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:44
msgid ""
"A method to **blend** two images. Transitions can take many forms, including "
"cuts, dissolves, and wipes."
msgstr ""
"Metoda za **spajanje** dviju slika. Prijelazi mogu imati različite oblike, "
"uključujući rezove, otapanja i brisanja."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
